00:00:41.553 --> 00:00:44.309
You tend to want to start in
the top left of the board.

00:00:44.309 --> 00:00:46.417
That way,
you have plenty of room to write.

00:00:46.417 --> 00:00:49.300
You want to make sure that you
leave space between lines,

00:00:49.300 --> 00:00:52.811
