go back and add lines in the middle.

00:00:52.811 --> 00:00:56.026
And then there were opportunities
where he would close out a tag and

00:00:56.026 --> 00:00:59.645
then he'd have to erase it and move
that closing down further and further,

00:00:59.645 --> 00:01:01.441
as we progress through the problem.

00:01:01.441 --> 00:01:05.545
So I would say,
give yourself more space for writing and

00:01:05.545 --> 00:01:08.614
don't close the tag until you're done.

